| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2862 — Recovery Inhibition (chaos)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7adbb7be-4e54-5b8a-8740-9ceff293a0cb"
